{"tid":2101553,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[大師兄返來了]蘇帥：般奴那球就是12碼  BBC:英超官方承認曼聯12碼與熱刺沒12碼都是誤判！","createTime":"2020-07-10T01:40:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T02:22:48.000Z","uid":103207,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ef024cdb0298480c34e36d7f03c177f3930ccb3c","tid":2101553,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T01:40:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2020/07/10/b/be086881599aa1b6baabd76f989a4712.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2020%2F07%2F10%2Fb%2Fbe086881599aa1b6baabd76f989a4712.jpg&h=a0a3fe4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://f.sinaimg.cn/sports/transform/624/w417h207/20200710/f293-iwasyei7881550.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ff.sinaimg.cn%2Fsports%2Ftransform%2F624%2Fw417h207%2F20200710%2Ff293-iwasyei7881550.gif&h=f8a289a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  英超第34輪，曼聯作客3-0輕取維拉。賽後紅魔教練蘇斯克查接受採訪，回應了12碼爭議判罰，並稱讚了球隊的表現。<br />\n<br />\n  上半場第26分鐘，般奴-費南迪斯突入禁區與維拉後衛孔薩發生衝撞倒地，球證判射12碼，費南迪斯主射命中幫助曼聯首開紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n  <span class=\"red\">這個12碼判罰引發了很大爭議，包括紅魔名宿艾夫拿、堅尼、舒米高在內的眾多體育專業人士認為不應判射12碼，但蘇斯克查表達了相反的意見。蘇斯克查說：「我認為那次犯規就是12碼，維拉後衛出腳了，費南迪斯做出了一個精彩的馬賽迴旋動作，然後他與後衛發生了碰撞，我認為這就是一個12碼。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2020/07/10/e/ebb6dead6474f2e62a8db273d3dd287f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2020%2F07%2F10%2Fe%2Febb6dead6474f2e62a8db273d3dd287f.jpg&h=539ea3c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  BBC的丹-獲加在Twitter上透露，他和英超比賽中心進行了聯絡，得到了關於週四晚三場英超聯賽判罰的反饋。<br />\n<br />\n  獲加在Twitter上寫道：<br />\n<br />\n  「我們和英超比賽中心溝通，他們確認：<br />\n<br />\n <span class=\"red\">費南迪斯的12碼：錯誤判罰，應該被取消；<br />\n<br />\n  禾特普斯的12碼：錯誤判罰，應該被取消；<br />\n<br />\n  簡尼沒有判12碼：錯誤判罰，應該是12碼。</span>」"},{"pid":"6add68acbe3d48213bd61c30487d0741a375da92","tid":2101553,"uid":7043,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T01:42:40.000Z","msg":"有埋片都可以判錯既真係得英超先做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9272a62d54d4d56e83969c2b21c00ec19a57f612","tid":2101553,"uid":30145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T01:42:44.000Z","msg":"精彩的馬賽迴旋動作<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f830f4e23820a05a1351accec60c481c45df284","tid":2101553,"uid":120575,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T01:43:59.000Z","msg":"英超var<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />判三場三場都錯<br />\n咁哂時間睇黎做乜"},{"pid":"112c045161a6e47acc6a51c67094a74d27240d9a","tid":2101553,"uid":18638,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T01:45:10.000Z","msg":"曼聯差唔多場場都有12碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d87a22c709141d2d8152afd0a7e8ed222f5f914e","tid":2101553,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"112c045161a6e47acc6a51c67094a74d27240d9a","tid":2101553,"uid":18638,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T01:45:10.000Z","msg":"曼聯差唔多場場都有12碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T01:46:41.000Z","msg":"好似3場先有1球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e7dc1231ce2b4ed8c22719312d62dfba32ae7be","tid":2101553,"uid":107405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f830f4e23820a05a1351accec60c481c45df284","tid":2101553,"uid":120575,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T01:43:59.000Z","msg":"英超var<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /